@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Flight Control Operator" as FCO
participant ":System" as System
participant ":Monthly Report Generator" as MonthlyReportGenerator
participant ":Monthly Statistics Data Source" as DataSource
participant ":Report Template" as ReportTemplate
participant ":Report File" as ReportFile

activate FCO

FCO -> System : Requests monthly statistics report

activate System
System --> FCO : Requests month and year
deactivate System

FCO -> System : Provides month and year

activate System
System --> System : Check if FCO is authenticated and authorized
System --> System : Validate month and year

alt month and year are valid

    System -> MonthlyReportGenerator : Generate monthly report(month, year)

    activate MonthlyReportGenerator

    MonthlyReportGenerator -> DataSource : Collect monthly statistics(month, year)

    activate DataSource
    DataSource --> MonthlyReportGenerator : Monthly statistics data
    deactivate DataSource

    MonthlyReportGenerator -> ReportTemplate : Apply common branding and structure

    activate ReportTemplate
    ReportTemplate --> MonthlyReportGenerator : Branded report structure
    deactivate ReportTemplate

    MonthlyReportGenerator --> MonthlyReportGenerator : Build report sections
    MonthlyReportGenerator --> MonthlyReportGenerator : Build tables and graphics

    MonthlyReportGenerator -> ReportFile : Save report to file

    activate ReportFile
    ReportFile --> MonthlyReportGenerator : Report file reference
    deactivate ReportFile

    MonthlyReportGenerator --> System : Monthly report generated
    deactivate MonthlyReportGenerator

    System --> FCO : Display report generation confirmation

else month or year are invalid

    System --> FCO : Display invalid reporting period message

else data collection or file generation fails

    System --> FCO : Display report generation error

end

deactivate System
deactivate FCO

@enduml